io.gearpump.cluster.appmaster

Class ExecutorSystemScheduler

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.gearpump.cluster.appmaster.ExecutorSystemScheduler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    akka.actor.Actor

    public class ExecutorSystemScheduler
extends java.lang.Object
implements akka.actor.Actor
    ExecutorSystem is also a type of resource, this class schedules ExecutorSystem for AppMaster. AppMaster can use this class to directly request a live executor actor systems. The communication in the background with Master and Worker is hidden from AppMaster.

    Please use ExecutorSystemScheduler.props() to construct this actor
